data.description: Back on the Market at no fault of seller! Welcome to the peace and quiet in the country with this beautiful built custom home on 11+ acres. It has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with a bonus room located upstairs. 2 of the rooms are joined by a jack and jill bath. The kitchen has beautiful custom cabinets and granite countertops. Off the kitchen is a formal dining room. The master is located on the opposite side of the house from the other 3 bedrooms. The pond is stocked and ready to be enjoyed. Located away from the home is a small metal structure that is currently being used as a kennel. Individual kennel panels will not stay with structure. Preapproval required for showing. Call Michelle at 912-213-0316 for appointment.
